{"tid":2013331,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"去少幾次日本都救到海洋公園啦！","createTime":"2020-05-12T08:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T11:17:44.000Z","uid":41846,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7b61374ade6b0485667dcb5b151745447b2fed","tid":2013331,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"劉鳴煒：未來半年將重新檢視海洋公園定位<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園陷入財困，政府向立法會財委會申請撥款54億元。海洋公園董事局副主席劉鳴煒表示，海洋公園是港人43年來的集體回憶，公園有7,500隻動物，相信港人都不想公園倒閉。他指，撥款將用於海洋公園未來12個月營運開支及還債，未來半年會與政府跨部門重新檢視未來定位，將有很大轉變。<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴煒又說，海洋公園自1月以來減少了100萬遊客人次，收入減少3至4億元，而未來入境香港的旅客屬哪類型等情況仍未可知，所以需時研究及檢討。<br />\n<br />\n另外，現任海洋公園行政總裁李繩宗將於今年7月退休，劉鳴煒指正全球招聘行政總裁，相信董事局通過後會公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%8A%89%E9%B3%B4%E7%85%92%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%87%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E6%AA%A2%E8%A6%96%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D-218383?fbclid=IwAR0nSi_dDXYFeVyuixkOrGhZn0P4SPxNnu2pBJb6r5_HMXSfbWhD5PWJZTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%25B3%25B4%25E7%2585%2592%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25B4%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25BD%258D-218383%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0nSi_dDXYFeVyuixkOrGhZn0P4SPxNnu2pBJb6r5_HMXSfbWhD5PWJZTs&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=14244297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%8A%89%E9%B3%B4%E7%85%92%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%87%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E6%AA%A2%E8%A6%96%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D-218383?fbclid=IwAR0nSi_dDXYFeVyuixkOrGhZn0P4SPxNnu2pBJb6r5_HMXSfbWhD5PWJZTs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n要立法會撥納稅人54億元？咁你身家幾百億，<br />\n去少幾次日本都救得返海洋公園啦，<br />\n使乜要拎納稅人嘅錢填呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01b2fb77a2b0b27320ca3d2baf57dbed3f1b440","tid":2013331,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"152dd54703193fd82d779818e38793866b168b10","tid":2013331,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"7500隻動物比人標左參咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb32cfc584b775e2a2957e2da6d10d083b711d41","tid":2013331,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"152dd54703193fd82d779818e38793866b168b10","tid":2013331,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"7500隻動物比人標左參咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"熊貓要送返去NMSLand。"},{"pid":"ec17416d1ffc9d23b6ce49252e11ab6e6ebb1068","tid":2013331,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16a64223cb61eb09343253480792fe904922ce8","tid":2013331,"uid":358086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:47:51.000Z","msg":"去少幾次日本都唔去海洋公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />滿地蝗"},{"pid":"3429775a667dde8839c9fa0ce297f925a3a8abb0","tid":2013331,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"揾支那錢就叻<br />\n<br />\n之前揾咁多 冇庫儲咩 定係高層條數太貴？"},{"pid":"2b25f6f5ed61e04472b44c716f3c88f148be47a5","tid":2013331,"uid":273627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"